4-10-06%2018%3A59%3A02.png"}], "short_description": "Everyone knows that the ancient Hebrews used to write on scrolls. Colloquially referred to as \"sticks\", \"The Sierra Bible\" offers the inspireable, open-minded Bible-lover a unique opportunity to read both the \"Stick of Joseph\", as well as \"The Stick of Judah.\"\r\n\r\nHence no matter if one chooses to believe Ezekiel 37:17-27 or not - the author of this software (R. A. Nagy) felt inspired to write this freeware to allow others to discover if - like himself - they too might be able to get a fuzzy-warm feeling by reading the pair of 'scrolls' together.\r\n\r\nIndeed, in a world where most of Christendom will not even recognize our common, Jesus-commanded need to repent & become perfect, why should anyone expect to find any type of agreement over the words of Ezekiel? \r\n\r\n(See the Homepage link for more information!)\r\n\r\nNote: If you prefer to read ONLY the King James Version of The Bible, then download \"The Classic Scriptures\" from https://sourceforge.net/projects/classicbible/ with our blessing!", "shortname": "sierrabible", "socialnetworks": [{"accounturl": "https://twitter.com/r_a_nagy", "socialnetwork": "Twitter"}, {"accounturl": "https://www.facebook.com/TheSierraBible", "socialnetwork": "Facebook"}], "status": "active", "summary": "The Sierra Bible Contains The King James Bible + The Book Of Mormon", "tools": [{"label": "Files", "mount_point": "files", "name": "files"}, {"label": "Summary", "mount_point": "summary", "name": "summary", "sourceforge_group_id": 2018476}, {"label": "Reviews", "mount_point": "reviews", "name": "reviews"}, {"label": "Support", "mount_point": "support", "name": "support"}, {"label": "Tickets", "mount_point": "tickets", "name": "tickets"}, {"label": "Activity", "mount_point": "activity", "name": "activity"}], "url": "http://sourceforge.net/p/sierrabible/", "video_url": null}
